'''Anouschka Izmirlian''' is a gemologist who evaluates and appraises gemstones for clients in [[New York City]]. From 1999 to 2004, she was a counselor at the [[Armenians|Armenian]] Mission to the [[United Nations]].

She is the daughter of Helena and Dikran S. Izmirlian of [[Geneva]]. Her father is the chairman and chief executive of Alimenta, a Geneva commodities trading company.{{citation needed|date=February 2013}}

She was formerly married to John Demsey.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/07/29/fashion/weddings/29izmirlian.html?_r=2&oref=slogin&|title=Anouschka Izmirlian and John Demsey|publisher="[[The New York Times]]''|accessdate=28 February 2013}}</ref>

